## 🎯 Quick Triggers

| Keywords | Behavior | Role |
|----------|----------|------|
| start task, begin work | `behaviors.getForTask` | 📖 Student |
| MCP tool, MCP server, IDE extension | `behavior_prefer_mcp_tools` | 📖 Student |
| secret, credential, API key, token | `behavior_prevent_secret_leaks` | 📖 Student |
| test, lint, pre-commit, push | `behavior_run_tests_before_push` | 📖 Student |
| docs, README, API reference | `behavior_update_docs_after_changes` | 📖 Student |
| hardcoded, config, env var | `behavior_externalize_configuration` | 📖 Student |
| CORS, auth, security, access control | `behavior_lock_down_security_surface` | 📖 Student |
| code review, PR review | `behavior_conduct_code_review` | 🎓 Teacher |
| git, branch, merge, commit | `behavior_git_governance` | 📖 Student |
| pattern observed 3+ times | `behaviors.propose` | 🧠 Strategist |

