## ✅ Student Checklist (Default)

Use at task start and after major milestones.

| # | Action | Example |
|---|--------|---------|
| 1 | **Declare role** with rationale | `🎭 Role: Student` — Adding auth per established pattern |
| 2 | **Scan triggers**, list applicable behaviors | `🔗 Behaviors: behavior_prevent_secret_leaks` |
| 3 | **Execute** following behavior steps; cite behavior+role | `Following behavior_prevent_secret_leaks (Student)...` |
| 4 | **Validate** — run smallest relevant check | `pytest tests/test_auth.py` |
| 5 | **Summarize** work with behavior citations | `Completed: Added auth (Student, behavior_prevent_secret_leaks)` |
| 6 | **Scout patterns** — note recurring workarounds | `🔍 Pattern: Third time adding rate limiting manually` |
| 7 | **Escalate?** — if pattern occurs 3+ times | `⬆️ Escalating: Student → Strategist` |

